<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="301" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="301">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="301">
Mexico (new country record, Chiapas), Nicaragua, Panama, Colombia (
<bibRefCitation author="Gonzalez-Cordoba, M" journalOrPublisher="Revista Intropica" pageId="0" pageNumber="301" pagination="85 - 95" publicationUrl="https://revistas.unimagdalena.edu.co/index.php/intropica/article/view/1865" refId="B34" refString="Gonzalez-Cordoba, M, Zuniga, MC, Mosquera-Murillo, Z, Sanchez-Vasquez, S, 2016. Riqueza y distribucion de Elmidae (Insecta: Coleoptera: Byrrhoidea) en el Departamento del Choco, Colombia. Revista Intropica 11: 85 - 95, https://revistas.unimagdalena.edu.co/index.php/intropica/article/view/1865" title="Riqueza y distribucion de Elmidae (Insecta: Coleoptera: Byrrhoidea) en el Departamento del Choco, Colombia." url="https://revistas.unimagdalena.edu.co/index.php/intropica/article/view/1865" volume="11" year="2016">
<normalizedToken originalValue="González-Córdoba">Gonzalez-Cordoba</normalizedToken>
et al. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2021.739.1263" author="Linsky, M" journalOrPublisher="European Jounal of Taxonomy" pageId="0" pageNumber="301" pagination="1 - 35" refId="B52" refString="Linsky, M, Ciamporova-Zatovicova, Z, Ciampor, F, 2021. A revision of Onychelmis Hinton, 1941 (Coleoptera: Elmidae), with description of new species, DNA barcoding and notes on the geography of the genus. European Jounal of Taxonomy 739: 1 - 35, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2021.739.1263" title="A revision of Onychelmis Hinton, 1941 (Coleoptera: Elmidae), with description of new species, DNA barcoding and notes on the geography of the genus." url="https://doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2021.739.1263" volume="739" year="2021">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Linský">Linsky</normalizedToken>
et al. 2021
</bibRefCitation>
). Previous altitudinal records were from 1,219 to 1,828 m (
<bibRefCitation author="Gonzalez-Cordoba, M" journalOrPublisher="Revista Intropica" pageId="0" pageNumber="301" pagination="85 - 95" publicationUrl="https://revistas.unimagdalena.edu.co/index.php/intropica/article/view/1865" refId="B34" refString="Gonzalez-Cordoba, M, Zuniga, MC, Mosquera-Murillo, Z, Sanchez-Vasquez, S, 2016. Riqueza y distribucion de Elmidae (Insecta: Coleoptera: Byrrhoidea) en el Departamento del Choco, Colombia. Revista Intropica 11: 85 - 95, https://revistas.unimagdalena.edu.co/index.php/intropica/article/view/1865" title="Riqueza y distribucion de Elmidae (Insecta: Coleoptera: Byrrhoidea) en el Departamento del Choco, Colombia." url="https://revistas.unimagdalena.edu.co/index.php/intropica/article/view/1865" volume="11" year="2016">
<normalizedToken originalValue="González-Córdoba">Gonzalez-Cordoba</normalizedToken>
et al. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2021.739.1263" author="Linsky, M" journalOrPublisher="European Jounal of Taxonomy" pageId="0" pageNumber="301" pagination="1 - 35" refId="B52" refString="Linsky, M, Ciamporova-Zatovicova, Z, Ciampor, F, 2021. A revision of Onychelmis Hinton, 1941 (Coleoptera: Elmidae), with description of new species, DNA barcoding and notes on the geography of the genus. European Jounal of Taxonomy 739: 1 - 35, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2021.739.1263" title="A revision of Onychelmis Hinton, 1941 (Coleoptera: Elmidae), with description of new species, DNA barcoding and notes on the geography of the genus." url="https://doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2021.739.1263" volume="739" year="2021">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Linský">Linsky</normalizedToken>
et al. 2021
</bibRefCitation>
). In the present study, the species was found at levels 1 (670 m), 2 (934 m), and 3 (1,126-1,194 m).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
